{"tid":764475,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"日本海底金字塔，水底下內藏的古代人類文明","createTime":"2018-08-02T04:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T13:48:49.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"670d222e6f5ea61d6627552d181ac732c782dfca","tid":764475,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"日本海底金字塔，發現1.2萬前的象形文字，考古家：姆文明現世<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上世紀末，在日本琉球列島附近發現的一座海底遺蹟，很有可能會徹底顛覆人類文明的認知。<br />\n<br />\n2007年，日本琉球大學地質學家木村政昭在一次學術會議上，認為在日本與那國島附近海底發現的石頭城遺蹟，是一座如傳說中沉入大西洋的亞特蘭蒂斯島上一樣的古人類遺址。他可能是在2000年前一次大地震中沉入海底。這處遺蹟的稜角分明，其中一個如金字塔形狀結構矗立水中，另外還有一些碎石貌雕刻而成動物或者人像，許多日本科學家稱其為日本的「亞特蘭蒂斯」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.cj.sina.cn/articles/view/6535272756/18588593400100jmlx?cre=tianyi&amp;mod=pcpager_fintoutiao&amp;loc=36&amp;r=9&amp;doct=0&amp;rfunc=100&amp;tj=none&amp;tr=9&amp;vt=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.cj.sina.cn%2Farticles%2Fview%2F6535272756%2F18588593400100jmlx%3Fcre%3Dtianyi%26mod%3Dpcpager_fintoutiao%26loc%3D36%26r%3D9%26doct%3D0%26rfunc%3D100%26tj%3Dnone%26tr%3D9%26vt%3D4&d=TlYb0R5tA8yi7HBAaSqlrJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=9a953f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.cj.sina.cn/articles/view/6535272756/18588593400100jmlx?cre=tianyi&amp;mod=pcpager_fintoutiao&amp;loc=36&amp;r=9&amp;doct=0&amp;rfunc=100&amp;tj=none&amp;tr=9&amp;vt=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sohu.com/a/128789326_639253/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F128789326_639253%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=TlYb0R5tA8yi7HBAaSqlrJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=b56b205a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.sohu.com/a/128789326_639253/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-mo/history/6knexo3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-mo%2Fhistory%2F6knexo3.html&d=TlYb0R5tA8yi7HBAaSqlrJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=d905f94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://k